## 五、完整 CSS 模板

```css
/* ── Checkbox 基础 ── */
.cb {
  width: 18px; height: 18px;
  border-radius: 3px;
  border: 1.5px solid #dedfe3;
  background: #ffffff;
  display: grid; place-items: center;
  cursor: pointer; flex-shrink: 0;
  transition: border-color .12s, background .12s;
  position: relative;
}
.cb:hover:not(.disabled) { border-color: var(--pcv-brand); }

/* 选中 */
.cb.checked {
  background: var(--pcv-brand);
  border-color: var(--pcv-brand);
}
.cb.checked::after {
  content: '';
  width: 8px; height: 6px;
  border-left: 2px solid #fff;
  border-bottom: 2px solid #fff;
  transform: rotate(-45deg) translate(1px, 0px);
  display: block;
}

/* 半选 */
.cb.indeterminate {
  background: #ffffff;
  border-color: var(--pcv-brand);
}
.cb.indeterminate::after {
  content: '';
  width: 8px; height: 2px;
  background: var(--pcv-brand);
  border-radius: 1px;
  display: block;
}

/* 禁用 */
.cb.disabled {
  background: #f4f5f6;
  border-color: #dedfe3;
  cursor: not-allowed;
}
.cb.disabled.checked::after   { border-color: #b2b2b8; }
.cb.disabled.indeterminate::after { background: #b2b2b8; }
```

